pressMultiTitle:
Science and Technology Minister Shri Arjun Modhwadia Graces the event;

Chief Minister:;
- The 'Viksit Gujarat Data Center Policy 2026-29' will make Gujarat the best destination in the country for establishing data centers;
- Under the leadership of the Prime Minister, Gujarat is emerging as a key player in India's digital ecosystem.;
- This policy  implements to strengthen the State's digital economy.;

Deputy Chief Minister:;

- Dholera in Gujarat will become the world's largest "Data Center City.";
- The policy places special emphasis on sustainability by mandating the use of 51 percent green energy and ensuring water supply through desalination plants.
